data.description: BRILLIANT FLOORPLAN!  This well-maintained all-brick ranch offers a desirable layout that includes 4 large bedrooms, a bright open main living area, and is ready for you to move right in.  Highlights include a gorgeous master suite with dual walk-in closets, an office nook, whirlpool tub & walk-in shower, an open eat-in kitchen with granite countertops, breakfast bar & stainless steel appliances, a bright open main living with a high cathedral ceiling & LVP flooring (carpet in bedrooms only), and a relaxing back patio that overlooks the level fenced backyard.  Very convenient location that is just minutes from the airport, Alcoa, and all of the conveniences in downtown Maryville.  Less than 30 minutes from downtown Knoxville!
